data.description: **SELLER IS MOTIVATED** Welcome home to Ocean Neighbors, conveniently located minutes away from Folly Beach, downtown Charleston, shopping, restaurants and a public boat landing. This home features an open floor plan with eat in kitchen, a separate dining room, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, fireplace, recessed lighting, all NEW Windows (2018), NEW faux wood blinds and NEW roof (2021). As you walk in you will find to the left, the formal dining room, currently used as an office with hardwood floors, crown molding and wainscotting with chair railing. From there you step into the open main living area, consisting of the family room, with a gas fireplace, that flows into the eat-in dining area and kitchen, that has a breakfast bar for additional seating, new refrigerator, dishwasher andmicrowave.  The pantry with custom doors, laundry and a recently updated powder room complete the first floor. On the second floor you'll find a small landing at the top of the stairs, the Owners Suite, 3 more bedrooms and a guest bathroom.  The Owner's suite is large with tray ceiling and crown molding, new ceiling fan and walk-in closet.  The ensuite includes jetted garden tub, separate shower, more crown molding and water closet.  Bedrooms 2 & 3 are nice in size, gets lots of natural light and have new ceiling fans.  You will be impressed with the size of the 4th bedroom, that is split from the other rooms, and it could easily be used as an entertainment/play/workout area. A guest full bath and linen closet complete this floor. In the backyard, you have a screened in porch, patio landing and a new living fence has been installed. This neighborhood also offers a 10-acre saltwater lake, which you could fish or launch a kayak from the covered community dock, and a playground. An added bonus, though the home does have flood insurance, it is now OPTIONAL. Per the seller, their lender no longer requires them to hold flood insurance since the FEMA remapping. It appears to be in Shaded X (500year flood plain). Come see your new home TODAY!
